snippet.title: Total War: WARHAMMER - Introducing... Cygor
snippet.description:
Cygors are distant cousins of the Minotaurs, but they have diverged significantly from their kin. Where once they could see the mortal world with two eyes, they can now only see the swirling Winds of Chaos with one. 

Beware the Beastmen... For more info on Call of the Beastmen: http://store.steampowered.com/app/404012/
